<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>A student must complete all admission requirements and register for resident credit before Advanced Placement credit may be reflected on the student's transcript.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://web.saumag.edu/ct/testing-center/advanced-placement/" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

